data.description: Welcome to 9100 S. Terry Rd, Mapleton, IL! This amazing ranch home sits on a private homesite with just under 6 acres and lake access! Don't miss out on the chance to call this 2300 sqft, 3 bedroom, 2 bath house, home.  Inside the home is a large living room with a fireplace and vaulted ceilings, a chef's dream kitchen with lots of cabinet storage and granite countertops, a dining room and a main floor laundry room.  Outside is a dream with an attached 2 stall garage, a detached 2 stall garage, a large deck overlooking the lake and a dock with a boat house, perfect for fishing! This home is sure to please and will not last long, schedule your private showing today!
